Per Aviem's suggestion, I removed `cacheCandidates` from the `SparkRunner`. I also did the style changes as requested by Amit.
@aviemzur THANKS so much for your suggestion, it's actually largely better.
@amitsela For the `PipelineRule`, I just quickly fixed the `StorageLevelTest` yesterday night. I'm suspecting something like a race condition (like the rule is evaluated after the options or so). I will take a deeper look today. Great to work together on this !
